  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やった！　できたぁ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yay! We did it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>these are text from 192</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたの？　何かいいこと、あったの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's wrong? Did something good happen?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>these are text from 192</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん！　ずっと書きためてたコレクター図鑑が
いっぱいになったんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yep! We've managed to gather a LOT of entries
in our Collector Compendium.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>these are text from 192</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごいや、&lt;Mel&gt;！　おめでとう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's pretty amazing, &lt;Mel&gt;! Congratulations!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>these are text from 192</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと♪　えへへ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehe...Thank you~</EnglishText>
      <Notes>these are text from 192</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>甘い！　甘いぜ！
フルーツポンチくらい甘い！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Easy! Super easy! So easy it's like
throwing a rock!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42584</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、何ぃ！　貴様は&lt;Dio&gt;ッ！
一体この図鑑のどこが甘いと言うんだぁー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>E-Easy!? &lt;Dio&gt;, when on earth was filling this
picture book easy!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クックックッ……　わからんか。
わからんか。わ・か・ら・ん・かァ〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heheheh...You don't know?
You really don't know...You don't know huh~</EnglishText>
      <Notes>can be reworded better</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ならば教えてやろう！　その図鑑にはこのおれが
幼少の頃に作った『万能高枝虫取り網』が無いのだぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then allow me to explain! This compendium contains the
all-powerful Legendary Peerless Insect Net.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>can definitely be reworded better
Need more context</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、なんだってー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A P-Peerless Insect Net!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……………………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>高いところに留まったセミなどを捕まえられる
優れものよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>O, high-grade cicadas who rests atop tall branches...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これならもうラクラク捕れます！
もう高いからってあきらめる必要はありません！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With this net, catching you will be as easy as breathing!
No long shall I weep once you move out of my reach!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さあ、この万能高枝虫取り網を使って、
セミをたくさん手に入れましょう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, let us capture a lot of cicadas with
this Legendary Peerless Insect Net,</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>効果には個人差があるのを気をつけないとね。
でも、私にも捕れるかしら？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahh, I see. It's a net that lets anyone capture anything.
Do you think I can also give it a whirl?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だーいじょうぶ！　長さも調節できるから安心！
さあ、次はあなたの番です！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Naturally! The length of the net can be adjusted
for anyone. Why don't you give it a shot?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……さ、行こっか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We should go...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_193_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Agreed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
